  <span class="nx">Down</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">DOWN</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">,</span>
  <span class="nx">Left</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">LEFT</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">,</span>
  <span class="nx">Right</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">RIGHT</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">,</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>лҳҗн•ң, л¬ёмһҗнҳ• мқҙл„ҳм—җлҠ” мҲ«мһҗнҳ• мқҙл„ҳкіјлҠ” лӢӨлҘҙкІҢ auto-incrementingмқҙ м—ҶлӢӨ.<br />
лҢҖмӢ  л””лІ„к№…мқ„ н•  л•Ң мҲ«мһҗнҳ• мқҙл„ҳмқҳ к°’мқҖ к°ҖлҒ” л¶ҲлӘ…нҷ•н•ҳкІҢ лӮҳмҳ¬ л•Ңк°Җ мһҲм§Җл§Ң л¬ёмһҗнҳ• мқҙл„ҳмқҖ н•ӯмғҒ лӘ…нҷ•н•ң к°’мқҙ лӮҳмҷҖм„ң мқҪкё° нҺён•ҳлӢӨ.</p>

<hr />

<h2 id="ліөн•©-мқҙл„ҳheterogeneous-enums">ліөн•© мқҙл„ҳ(Heterogeneous Enums)</h2>

<p>кё°мҲ м ҒмңјлЎң мқҙл„ҳм—җ л¬ёмһҗмҷҖ мҲ«мһҗлҘј нҳјн•©н•ҳм—¬ мғқм„ұ н•  мҲҳ мһҲлӢӨ.</p>

<div class="language-typescript highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kr">enum</span> <span class="nx">BooleanLikeHeterogeneousEnums</span> <span class="p">{</span>
  <span class="nx">No</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span>
